<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><id>https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=110&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0</id><title>HKDiscuss house</title><updated>2025-06-09T10:13:42.648904+00:00</updated><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=110&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0"/><generator uri="https://lkiesow.github.io/python-feedgen" version="1.0.0">python-feedgen</generator><subtitle>Latest articles</subtitle><entry><id>6fbc0b829201b3c7c8a9093ab6310400</id><title>🆘麗港城呎價跌穿1萬關口 2房險守5字頭</title><updated>2025-06-08T23:25:46+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-08T23:25:46+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572755867"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572755867"&gt;幾十年樓 早應該&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="62" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_o05.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3961558%2F%25E9%25BA%2597%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%2591%258E%25E5%2583%25B9%25E8%25B7%258C%25E7%25A9%25BF1%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%258F%25A3%25202%25E6%2588%25BF%25E9%259A%25AA%25E5%25AE%25885%25E5%25AD%2597%25E9%25A0%25AD%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=1255a39b3d390c933dd24cb7a16794af&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3961558/麗港城呎價跌穿1萬關口 2房險守5字頭?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;藍田麗港城本月至今暫錄得2宗成交，平均實用呎價跌穿萬元關口，最新報9859元。中原地產麗港城分區營業經理洪金興表示，麗港城7座中層B室，實用面積517平方呎，採兩房一廁間隔，單位座向東北方，望公園景，最初以540萬元放售，議價後降價32萬元或6%，以508萬元易手，折合實用呎價9826元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;據了解，原業主早於2006年1月以91.82萬元買入單位，持貨已經19年，現轉手賬面大幅獲利416.18萬元離場，單位升值逾4.5倍。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;[&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; 本帖最後由 叔叔要不要 於 2025-6-9 16:46 編輯 &lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31950826&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=21375212756846b3d6cc2153_09419534"/><published>2025-06-08T23:25:46+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>3976b611801ea545a8ec7cb1fc3697fe</id><title>太子道西/亞皆老街一帶傳統豪宅平均一萬蚊每呎！😍</title><updated>2025-06-09T00:20:54+08:00</updated><author><name>星星笑</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-09T00:20:54+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572756311"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572756311"&gt;好似勝豐園同碧麗閣，都是過千呎但千零萬就買到，好想買可惜冇錢！&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;😂&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31950868&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=21375212756846b3d6cc2153_09419534"/><published>2025-06-09T00:20:54+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>a63a6e28d1ad4fea4ffb798949199f0c</id><title>1000元就能租到一線無敵海景房 !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!</title><updated>2025-06-09T12:33:20+08:00</updated><author><name>花子果</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-09T12:33:20+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572761289"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572761289"&gt;香港人天堂&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="65" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_o03.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen="" class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8F-_ETeBGAE?wmode=transparent" wmode="Opaque"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.yo